OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will stay mostly dry in the
OL,6,Feast through the day with some bright
OL,7,For sunny spells and just the odd
OL,8,Fshower. Cloudier in the west with a
OL,9,Ffew showers. Windy.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FMostly dry with some bright
OL,12,Fspells at first but showers become
OL,13,Fmore frequent through the evening and
OL,14,Fovernight. Windy at times.
OL,15,
OL,16,CSaturday:FIt will stay mainly dry in
OL,17,FEastern Borders with some bright
OL,18,Fspells at times. Cloudier in the west
OL,19,Fwith some showers, becoming drier
OL,20,Flater in the day. Windy at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
